data.description: ASK ABOUT 1YR RATE BUYDOWN & APPRAISAL CREDIT! The largest home in this price range makes it the best value! This roomy home is ideally situated 2 minutes from freeways and 5 minutes from PSNS! Main level entry offers a spacious kitchen with granite counters and stainless appliances, open concept to the dining and living room spaces. All with high ceilings and an extra deep garage! Step out onto the back deck and enjoy the elements. Journey upstairs and tuck into the bedrooms. Upstairs laundry here too! One of the highlights is the huge bonus space downstairs. Fully finished basement level with access to the fully fenced back yard offers endless possibilities. Game room, theater room, library, coat and shoe room, dealer's choice!
